        "text": "re single pass not requiring entire tree: depends on language semantics: imagine LISP with hoisting, or even just js:\nSometimes you have to postpone at least some work, because used symbols so far are not \"declared yet\".\nWorst case scenario – all the code is a single dependency chain, where each node's analysis waits for some next one to complete (where peephole size = project size).",
